<h3 id="platform">Platform</h3>
<p>Kubernetes may run on Baremetal or Virtual Machines, there are not any limitations on this aspect, however, the platform we chose will set the operational aspects of our Kubernetes platform.</p>
<h4 id="baremetal">Baremetal</h4>
<p>Starting with baremetal, this kind of platform allow us dedicate all the compute resources from the hardware to our Kubernetes nodes. At first look, this may sound interesting from the performance perspective, however, if we check the operative or cost impact choosing a Baremetal platform, we can list some constraints:</p>















